@startuml US-15
title US-15 Admin Dashboard (System Stats)

actor Admin
boundary "Admin UI" as UI
control "AdminController" as ADC
control "StatsService" as SS
database "OrderRepository" as OR

Admin -> UI: Open dashboard
UI -> ADC: GET /admin/stats
ADC -> SS: getTotalSales()
SS -> OR: sumTotalAmountAllOrders()
OR --> SS: totalSales
SS --> ADC: totalSales
ADC --> UI: 200 OK + totalSales
UI --> Admin: Display total sales
@enduml
